    dc:description "Figure 10. Conidial morphology of Pestalotiopsis formosana (A, B NTUPPMCC 21 - 056), Pestalotiopsis trachycarpicola (C NTUPPMCC 18 - 160 D NTUPPMCC 21 - 055) and Neopestalotiopsis sp. (E NTUPPMCC 18 - 161), isolated from entomopathogenic fungi in this study. Scale bars: 20 μm (A-E)." ;
